  <description><![CDATA[<p>Enjoying a prime position overlooking the Clotes home-run piste, Hotel Chalet Del Sole is a traditional chalet style building in keeping with local mountain architecture. On a natural terrace overlooking the Susa valley, this simple hotel benefits from excellent views and a ski in/out location. The panoramic bar and restaurant serves authentic local fare and is the focal point of this laid back accommodation. Whilst piste-side, the resort bus stops outside to quickly ferry you to Sauze's charming centre throughout the day.</p>]]></description>
